<ol><li><b>Progressive wave</b>&nbsp;is sent out by the vibrator.<br></li><li>The crest&nbsp;<b>reverses its phase</b>&nbsp;when it reflects at the fixed ends, and</li><li><b>Travels back</b>&nbsp;along the string as a&nbsp;<b>trough</b>.<br></li><li>It&nbsp;<b>reflects and reverse phase</b>&nbsp;again, travelling away from the vibrator as a&nbsp;<b>crest</b>.</li></ol><div>If this crest is reinforced by a crest created by the vibrator, the amplitude of the wave is increased, and&nbsp;<u>a stationary wave is formed</u>.</div>